      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad usrahpahs Ionatans\nar sawahm Rohkahm un ar fa-\nwahm Rahjahm / un winna\nBrunnu-Nestejs winnam pak-\nkat:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee kritte preeksch Jo-\nnatann / un winna Brunnu-\nNestejs nokawe tohs pakkat win-\nxu/ ta ka schinni pirmâ Kaufcha-\nnâ/ Ionatans un winna Brun-\nnu-Nestejs pee diwiderifnits Wilh-\nreem nokawe/ tik ne weenu putś\nBirsuma Weetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tur ktua Drebbescha-\nna Lehgeri/Lankâ/ un starp teem\nLaudim/ ir tas Lehgeris/ ir tee\nGixrotaji paschi drebbeja / un ta\nSemme tribfeja/ jo ta bija wee-\nna Drebbeschana no Deewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad nu Saula Sargi\neeksch Gibejas Benjamixa redse-\nja/ ka/ rangi/ tas Pulks nosud-\nde/ isklihde un fakults tappa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls us teem\nLaudim/ kas pee winna bija/ lih-\ndsinajeetees jelle un raugajt/ kas\nno mums irr nogahjis/ tad tee\nlihdsinajahs/ un raugi Ionatans\nun winna Brunnu- Nestejs bija\nnohst.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls ns A-\nkiju: Atness to Deewa Schkirstu\nschurp/ (jo tas Deewa Schkirsts\nbija to Laiku pee teem Israëta\nBehrneem.)\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kamehr Sauls webt us\nto Preesteri runnaja/ tad ange-\ntas Trohffnis Wilisteru Lehgeri/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "un wairojahs/ tad fazzija Saul-\nus to Preesteri: Saturr taw-\nRohku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tappe Sauls un wis-\nsi Laudis/ kas pee winna bija fa-\ntaukti/ nn nahze kautees/ un rau-\ngi/ tur bija weena Sohbins pret-\nobtra / un bija leels Trohffnis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir tee Eebreeti/ kas zitt-\nkahrt pee teem Wilistereem biju-\ntchi/ nn ar teem bij eeksch Lehge-\nra apkahrt zehluschees / tee pasch-\narridsan pahrnahje pee Israëta/\nkas pee Saula un pee Ionata-\nna bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wisfi Israëta Wihi/kae-\nbij apflehpuschees us Eewräima-\nKalneem / kad tee dsirdeja tohe-\nWilisterus behgam/ dsinahs teem-\narrt eeksch Kaufchanas pakkat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta atpestija tas KUNGS\ntai Deenâ Israelu/un taKaufcha-\nna steepahs lihds Bet-Awenam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Israëta Wi ri no-\ngurre tai Deenâ / jo Sauls bija\nteem Laudim peekohdinajs/fazzt-\ndams: Nolahdehts latd irr tas-\nWihrs/ kas jeb ko ehdihs lihds-\nWakkaram / ka es pee faween-\nEnaidneekeemi atreebjohs/ tadeht-\nne baudija tee Laudis neneeka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wisfi Seinnes Lau-\ndis nahze Meschâ/ un tur bija\nMeddus Lankâ Wirii.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad uu tee Laudis Me-\nschâ nahze/ rangi/ tad tezzejatur\nMeddus. Bet ne weens likke fa-\nwu Rohkn pee fawas Wuttes/ jo\ntee Laudis bibjajahs preeksch tahs\nAplahdeschanas.\n"
    }
  ],
